---
title: Persian-Inspired Chickpea, Shrimp and Veggie Stew with Toasted Garlic Flatbreads
description: Middle Eastern spice-roasted carrots are the star of this warming tomato-based stew. Toasted almonds, shrimp and a spicy chili-garlic sauce are the perfect toppers for this crave-worthy dinner!
